message: Human Trafficking ‘the new crack cocaine,’ Bay Area police say. The FBI has identified the San Francisco Bay Area, including Santa Cruz and Monterey counties, as one of the three highest-intensity child sex trafficking regions in the country.

data.description: The FBI has identified the San Francisco Bay Area as one of the three highest-intensity child sex trafficking regions in the country.
data.title: Human trafficking, ‘the new crack cocaine,’ Bay Area police say
